result.title: Week of Code 30 [Hackerrank]
result.content:
Hello Coders!

The 30th edition of Week of Code is here. 7 interesting challenges (one challenge is unlocked each day). The contest commences on on 13th March 2017 at 07:00 UTC, You can sign up for the contest here.

Top 10 on leaderboard get cool HackerRank T Shirts

Please try all problems, Editorials will be available at the end of contest.

GL&HF
